flowPara.flowSpan: Get familiar with "good enough" research software development tools and practices (git, GitHub, Jupyter, reproducible enviroments, licensing, testing, ...).

flowRoot.flowPara: Interactive event series. You can join on your own, watch together with a team or join an in-person room (only some locations, see event page).
